comics.name: Chin Binh Hc ng
comics.description: Th k 21, tri t dung hp vi mt th gii khc, mt k nguyn ca Hm ngc bt u, ni trn ngp qui vt v cc cuc t kch ca nhng t Kch Gi. V mt c quan gio dc hng u ca Hn Quc  c lp thnh  nui dng cc nh mo him ny: Hc vin Chin Binh. Yoo Jaryong, mc d cu tng c xem l mt trong nhng nh mo him mnh nht Chu , nhng v b buc ti oan m cu phi i cn qut lu cc hm ngc  c tin tr vin ph cho cha. Mt ngi Yoo Yaryong v tnh gp  ni vi cu ta rng: Cu, hy n Hc Vin Chin Binh y l cu chuyn v mt chng trai tr, ngi  nh mt c gic m, giu i xut thn, ang mt ln na tm li chnh mnh.
